{"tid":920301,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖慎入)有冇人試過全身出滿紅疹？","createTime":"2018-11-28T17:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T08:25:55.000Z","uid":111474,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ae5f8b3a56c096a61010c9f3a518a906ba73b1","tid":920301,"uid":111474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T17:21:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/048c85d8033ee77492ed8e420852d473.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F048c85d8033ee77492ed8e420852d473.jpg&d=BEUgg9UfG23NtCXPAgLafwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=70a2afd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/048c85d8033ee77492ed8e420852d473.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n認真求教 想講笑既巴打唔該高抬貴手唔好係呢度講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇過皮膚科話係濕疹 另外排緊d皮膚科要半個月、2個月先睇到<br />\n<br />\n起左大約一個月<br />\n如果唔特登R 唔會好痕  但R落會幾痕下<br />\n亦都唔似濕疹咁會出水同d皮會好緊<br />\n揸過類固醇(專科俾)基本上無好轉<br />\n身背4枝都有 面就冇<br />\n<br />\nGoogle過有d似玫瑰糠疹<br />\n想問下有冇人知係咩事"},{"pid":"738008d92f18a7223d01618ec0c2baf0a789d7ab","tid":920301,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3a92a371b5e58a0fad670bc67d8a75f67f5da32","tid":920301,"uid":150510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"係咪轉季著放左衣櫃好耐嘅衫先開始起？<br />\n塵蟎都可以搞到你咁<br />\n不過如果成個月個人乾淨返都應該退到<br />\n<br />\n最緊要忍手唔好R傷<br />\n希望你快啲好返"},{"pid":"88699ade9f1485dd6509c8b950347a4910e79f79","tid":920301,"uid":111474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"738008d92f18a7223d01618ec0c2baf0a789d7ab","tid":920301,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"其實唔R佢係冇咩感覺<br />\n唔似濕疹咁周身唔聚財咁<br />\n唔會點影響生活 係樣衰d<br />\n所以應該唔使打針住"},{"pid":"ad5e885c982a11ffca01648b2b6f56726ad16548","ti